      "description": "Social media platforms will comply with various international data protection laws, such as the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) in the European Union, to ensure that user privacy is protected across borders. Adhering to these regulations will help platforms maintain a global user base while ensuring privacy and security.",
      "examples": ["GDPR compliance", "Privacy Shield certification"]
    }
  }
